00:35:20,037 --> 00:35:22,706
Right, when men see you biting a quail,

505
00:35:22,915 --> 00:35:24,875
they'll naturally hold and hug you.

506
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:29,880
Now you can put your head
on their shoulders.

507
00:35:40,390 --> 00:35:41,808
What for?

508
00:35:42,976 --> 00:35:44,603
Excuse me, my job requires this.

509
00:35:44,770 --> 00:35:46,522
You must stop doing that!

510
00:35:46,897 --> 00:35:48,524
Superficially it's all.

511
00:35:48,690 --> 00:35:52,194
If we go further, I must then ask you
about your first love.

512
00:35:53,403 --> 00:35:54,738
I never have first love.

513
00:35:55,030 --> 00:35:56,782
Everyone has first love.

514
00:35:56,907 --> 00:35:58,242
I said I never have one.

515
00:35:59,743 --> 00:36:02,329
You must have some unforgettable memory.

516
00:36:02,663 --> 00:36:03,664
No.

517
00:36:13,924 --> 00:36:16,510
Or you must have heard someone
say something you can never forget.

518
00:36:17,928 --> 00:36:19,054
Never!

519
00:36:19,179 --> 00:36:21,139
I hope I can be with you forever.

520
00:36:21,932 --> 00:36:24,726
Promise me, let me take care of you
for the rest of your life.

521
00:36:44,079 --> 00:36:46,748
Then you must have
unforgettable experience.

522
00:36:47,624 --> 00:36:48,709
Never!

523
00:36:52,421 --> 00:36:55,591
Being club girl? Didn't say
you'll take care of me?

524
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,760
How come I have money
if you don't work as club girl?

525
00:36:58,927 --> 00:37:01,054
How can I take care of you
if I have no money?

526
00:37:02,931 --> 00:37:07,060
Now, imagine
I'm your first boyfriend lover.

527
00:37:19,907 --> 00:37:24,328
Sau, on the night of your play,
I was engaged in a transaction.

528
00:37:24,495 --> 00:37:27,164
So I was too busy to come, sorry.

529
00:37:27,414 --> 00:37:29,458
- Was there good response?
- Sure.

530
00:37:29,666 --> 00:37:32,753
It's good then.
I will surely come next time.

531
00:37:33,587 --> 00:37:39,718
Someone're shooing kids karaoke,
you aren't one of them?

532
00:37:39,885 --> 00:37:42,012
I've things to see you, excuse me.

533
00:37:42,221 --> 00:37:45,432
Take me new boy
to collect protection money for me.

534
00:37:45,682 --> 00:37:48,685
Help me improve his appearance...
About the way he speaks?

535
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:53,565
Right, that's it,
you won't refuse my request, right?

536
00:37:55,442 --> 00:37:56,527
Thanks for teaching me.

537
00:37:58,987 --> 00:38:00,113
Over there.

538
00:38:00,364 --> 00:38:02,407
Being a triad member...

539
00:38:02,574 --> 00:38:04,701
you must have a unique appearance.

540
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:06,662
It's right
you have a gold chain with you.

541
00:38:06,829 --> 00:38:11,375
You must try to look furious and severe.
Try it.

542
00:38:12,918 --> 00:38:16,213
More furious. Show some anger.

543
00:38:17,881 --> 00:38:19,299
Wrath.

544
00:38:26,223 --> 00:38:27,516
Throw that nibble away.

545
00:38:27,724 --> 00:38:29,977
This is it,
you know what you're going to say?

546
00:38:30,102 --> 00:38:30,894
I seem to know.

547
00:38:31,019 --> 00:38:33,480
Good, I'll remind you from time to time
in this dim place.

548
00:38:42,156 --> 00:38:43,866
Tong, over here a bit, right, cheer up.

549
00:38:44,032 --> 00:38:45,951
- Shooting a movie?
- What is it?

550
00:38:48,203 --> 00:38:49,288
I forget already.

551
00:38:58,255 --> 00:38:59,673
You know, HK is in economic recession.

552
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:02,509
And being hit by financial storm,
it's all because of the 'Ross'.

553
00:39:02,718 --> 00:39:03,719
There are many factors.

554
00:39:03,886 --> 00:39:06,138
Now the S.E.
Asia collapses in economics...

555
00:39:06,346 --> 00:39:08,891
and that infects HK too.

556
00:39:09,099 --> 00:39:11,768
Those enterprises suffer much.

557
00:39:12,019 --> 00:39:16,773
The worse is there'll be
global economics recession soon.

558
00:39:16,982 --> 00:39:18,400
You have a view in economics.

559
00:39:18,609 --> 00:39:20,736
I majored Economics in HKU.

560
00:39:20,944 --> 00:39:22,362
Did you? I graduated this year.

561
00:39:22,488 --> 00:39:25,365
Did you? I graduated in 1996,
this is my name card.

562
00:39:25,824 --> 00:39:27,993
- You're my senior, nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

563
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:30,829
- How come you shoot kids karaoke?
- I can't help.

564
00:39:36,210 --> 00:39:37,211
What are you doing now?

565
00:39:37,377 --> 00:39:39,713
Nothing, I fool with triad members.

566
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:42,216
Seeing you shooting movie here,
I come to collect protection money.

567
00:39:43,050 --> 00:39:45,636
Brother Kei,
someone collects protection money.

568
00:39:47,346 --> 00:39:48,764
Who collects protection money?

569
00:39:58,565 --> 00:40:00,400
- Economics in HK is now...
- Is it you?

570
00:40:03,111 --> 00:40:04,321
Good.

571
00:40:10,619 --> 00:40:12,579
Bastard,
what triad groups are you come from?

572
00:40:35,727 --> 00:40:37,145
Dare you to fool me?

573
00:40:48,198 --> 00:40:49,408
Fix him!

574
00:40:52,244 --> 00:40:54,371
Kill you!

575
00:40:54,997 --> 00:40:58,167
Go to hell! Bastard...

576
00:41:01,295 --> 00:41:04,173
Dare you play with my bird?
Don't you know me?

577
00:41:04,923 --> 00:41:06,884
Don't come near...

578
00:41:08,135 --> 00:41:09,052
It hurts...

579
00:41:09,261 --> 00:41:12,681
Don't talk with me,
pretend we're at a duel.

580
00:41:13,265 --> 00:41:15,851
Make a call...pretend calling for help.

581
00:41:20,397 --> 00:41:22,024
I want to go home.

582
00:41:22,149 --> 00:41:24,193
You must act on until I shout cut.

583
00:41:24,359 --> 00:41:27,654
- You must be profession.
- I want to go home.

584
00:41:27,779 --> 00:41:28,697
It's a day.

585
00:41:30,407 --> 00:41:31,492
They're gone.

586
00:41:31,867 --> 00:41:33,410
Don't be afraid, they're gone, all gone.

587
00:41:33,827 --> 00:41:36,830
Take a chopper and a rush there,
get some fame.

588
00:41:49,927 --> 00:41:50,719
What's wrong?

589
00:41:50,844 --> 00:41:52,387
That scoundrel is still there.

590
00:41:52,554 --> 00:41:56,058
Concentrate! you're scoundrel too,
show some anger!

591
00:41:56,225 --> 00:41:58,143
I want to eat ice-cream.

592
00:41:58,644 --> 00:42:01,104
Bastard! Show some anger!

593
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:18,205
You needn't do that.

594
00:42:32,386 --> 00:42:34,137
Forget it, I fear you now.

595
00:42:42,354 --> 00:42:44,481
What's up? You acted very well.

596
00:42:46,984 --> 00:42:48,193
What has happened?

597
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:50,404
He acted really well to get this.

598
00:42:51,029 --> 00:42:52,573
He managed to collect $20.

599
00:42:52,698 --> 00:42:54,199
Why are you still crying?

600
00:42:54,366 --> 00:42:56,785
You managed to get $20 protection money
in front of a temple.

601
00:42:56,994 --> 00:42:58,620
You're making a fame for yourself.

602
00:42:58,745 --> 00:43:00,164
You do look like a hero.

603
00:43:00,372 --> 00:43:03,667
Keep the image and use it
to collect protection money now.

604
00:43:03,709 --> 00:43:06,086
Brother Sau, you're competent, great!

605
00:43:06,253 --> 00:43:07,045
You're flattering me.

606
00:43:07,129 --> 00:43:10,007
Let's get a feast, with this $20.

607
00:43:12,259 --> 00:43:15,262
What are you laughing at?
Keep this image, got it?

608
00:43:15,470 --> 00:43:18,640
- Stop laughing! Cry!
- Stop laughing! Cry!

609
00:43:18,932 --> 00:43:21,310
Be good, cry, cry now!

610
00:43:21,435 --> 00:43:22,769
What are you laughing at! Cry now!

611
00:43:22,853 --> 00:43:24,563
That under-graduate hold two choppers.

612
00:43:24,813 --> 00:43:27,691
And rushes over
while crying and shouting.

613
00:43:27,858 --> 00:43:30,736
He's crying loudly.

614
00:43:30,861 --> 00:43:34,156
He is capable
to play the spirit of a triad member.

615
00:43:34,364 --> 00:43:35,991
Thanks for his persistence,

616
00:43:36,116 --> 00:43:38,452
He managed to get $20
as a protection money.

617
00:43:38,577 --> 00:43:39,661
What are you talking about?

618
00:43:39,912 --> 00:43:41,747
Persistence, Aunt Ha.

619
00:43:41,872 --> 00:43:43,916
I believe that I'm a good actor,
do me a favour please.

620
00:43:44,082 --> 00:43:46,001
I have new experience
about holding choppers.

621
00:43:46,210 --> 00:43:47,628
I'd play well in a kung fu movie.

622
00:43:47,711 --> 00:43:50,380
What?
You've brought enough trouble to me.

623
00:43:50,547 --> 00:43:53,425
How dare you asking me for help?
Go away!

624
00:43:56,386 --> 00:43:57,804
Sorry, Brother Sunny, he's leaving now.

625
00:43:57,971 --> 00:44:00,641
I've looking for you.
Make up and get ready.

626
00:44:00,891 --> 00:44:02,017
Thanks!

627
00:44:03,185 --> 00:44:04,520
Director, we've found the stunt man.

628
00:44:04,686 --> 00:44:06,522
You said you can't find one just then?
You're wasting my time!

629
00:44:06,688 --> 00:44:07,689
I've found one now.

630
00:44:07,856 --> 00:44:08,774
You have no problem?

631
00:44:08,941 --> 00:44:12,027
No problem, I'll try my best to be
the stunt man for Sister Cuckoo.

632
00:44:12,236 --> 00:44:13,320
Director, no problem.

633
00:44:13,695 --> 00:44:15,155
Light the fire.

634
00:44:15,280 --> 00:44:16,073
Director.

635
00:44:16,281 --> 00:44:17,616
Beside responding with the hot fire,

636
00:44:17,783 --> 00:44:19,827
Can I show an expression
of cool loneliness?

637
00:44:20,118 --> 00:44:21,119
As you like,

638
00:44:21,286 --> 00:44:24,081
As long as you don't turn your face
to the camera, get it?

639
00:44:24,164 --> 00:44:25,207
Got it.

640
00:44:25,249 --> 00:44:27,709
Light the fire, just don't move.

641
00:44:30,087 --> 00:44:31,421
Ready.

642
00:44:31,713 --> 00:44:33,549
Who put the pigeons here?

643
00:44:33,715 --> 00:44:34,800
Director, I put them here intentionally.

644
00:44:34,967 --> 00:44:36,718
There're pigeons here in our last shot.

645
00:44:36,844 --> 00:44:39,930
If the pigeons fly,
they'll stir up the fire.

646
00:44:40,138 --> 00:44:42,057
- Take them away.
- Director...

647
00:44:43,100 --> 00:44:45,561
The mood of this shot will be better
if the pigeons are there.

648
00:44:45,727 --> 00:44:47,020
How much better?

649
00:44:48,397 --> 00:44:51,692
It's hard to say,
it's something abstract.

650
00:44:51,900 --> 00:44:53,318
Anyway, the mood will be better.

651
00:44:53,861 --> 00:44:55,195
Put them up and let's see the effect.

652
00:44:57,531 --> 00:44:59,449
That stunt man mustn't turn his head!

653
00:44:59,992 --> 00:45:01,285
Director, how do you like it?

654
00:45:01,743 --> 00:45:02,953
It's a bit better.

655
00:45:03,370 --> 00:45:07,708
Let's try the effect
with the pigeon's head towards me.

656
00:45:10,085 --> 00:45:13,046
Now put the pigeon's tail towards me.

657
00:45:15,632 --> 00:45:17,885
Take it away. Ready.

658
00:45:18,302 --> 00:45:19,928
It's better without the pigeons,
take it away.

659
00:45:20,596 --> 00:45:21,805
Ready.

660
00:45:21,972 --> 00:45:24,016
Where's my lighter?

661
00:45:27,269 --> 00:45:28,478
Man, bring me a lighter?

662
00:45:28,604 --> 00:45:29,646
Director, here it is.

663
00:45:29,771 --> 00:45:30,981
- Really?
- Yes.

664
00:45:31,190 --> 00:45:32,608
- It works?
- Yes.

665
00:45:35,360 --> 00:45:36,778
Hurry, quick, ready!

666
00:45:37,404 --> 00:45:39,531
Ready, keep your posture, don't move.

667
00:45:39,698 --> 00:45:41,783
Roll, action!

668
00:45:43,327 --> 00:45:44,536
What is it?

669
00:45:49,666 --> 00:45:52,044
What's wrong with you?
You screwed up every time!

670
00:45:52,503 --> 00:45:53,795
Sorry, Brother Sunny,
it's very hot here.

671
00:45:53,962 --> 00:45:56,131
I've told you already,
and you said no problem.

672
00:45:56,298 --> 00:45:57,341
Shall we try again?

673
00:45:57,633 --> 00:45:59,384
Again? Get a smarter guy.

674
00:45:59,593 --> 00:46:01,011
It's your fault, Sunny?

675
00:46:01,345 --> 00:46:03,805
Sorry, Director. Get lost!

676
00:46:06,099 --> 00:46:09,269
I've tried my best to help you,
don't ever come again.

677
00:46:10,437 --> 00:46:11,438
Just then...

678
00:46:11,605 --> 00:46:13,357
Do you smell BBQ chicken wing?

679
00:46:13,482 --> 00:46:16,235
I've sacrificed my arm
just for this movie.

680
00:46:16,443 --> 00:46:18,362
Unit Manager, give him an over-cooked
chicken wing rice lunch box.

681
00:46:18,529 --> 00:46:19,404
OK.

682
00:46:19,613 --> 00:46:20,948
You, don't ever let me see him again...

683
00:46:21,156 --> 00:46:22,241
Or I'll fire you instantly as well!

684
00:46:22,449 --> 00:46:23,450
Aunt Ha...

685
00:46:23,575 --> 00:46:26,245
Don't ask me anymore. Brother Sunny!

686
00:46:26,495 --> 00:46:27,955
Chicken wings rice.

687
00:46:29,498 --> 00:46:33,126
Let me see which is over-cooked,
the chicken wing or your arm.

688
00:46:33,544 --> 00:46:35,504
Not over-cooked, go away now.

689
00:46:36,338 --> 00:46:38,298
- Brother Sunny said I have a lunch box.
- Go away!

690
00:46:41,385 --> 00:46:42,594
Extras are human being as well.

691
00:46:42,845 --> 00:46:44,304
What? Repeat it loudly!

692
00:46:44,471 --> 00:46:45,472
Aren't extras human?

693
00:46:45,639 --> 00:46:46,849
Why must you always jump in me?

694
00:46:47,015 --> 00:46:49,977
- You want to know the reason?
- I want to know the reason.

695
00:46:50,143 --> 00:46:52,396
Because you're not entitled
to eat this lunch box!

696
00:46:54,898 --> 00:46:57,568
You thought you're talented
and teach others acting.

697
00:46:57,734 --> 00:46:59,486
You always talk about theory.

698
00:46:59,653 --> 00:47:02,531
You teach someone to be a triad member
and collect protection money.

699
00:47:03,740 --> 00:47:06,118
You're indeed insulting
the word 'acting'!

700
00:47:06,577 --> 00:47:08,537
Don't shout on, let's get to work.

701
00:47:09,997 --> 00:47:14,334
You talk about 'acting' in front of me?
Shit!

702
00:47:16,712 --> 00:47:18,046
Damn it!

703
00:47:19,089 --> 00:47:21,425
They dare to collect protection money
from those 2 ice-cream cars?

704
00:47:21,633 --> 00:47:23,552
I'm the protector
of those 2 ice-cream cars.

705
00:47:23,760 --> 00:47:25,596
They don't respect me at all.

706
00:47:25,762 --> 00:47:27,598
Men, get some weapons
and teach them a lesson.

707
00:47:27,764 --> 00:47:29,308
Sau, come with us.

708
00:47:29,558 --> 00:47:31,685
You can experience
how we fight for our right,

709
00:47:31,852 --> 00:47:33,687
and keep guard for us as well.
Men, let's go.

710
00:47:33,979 --> 00:47:36,648
Little Hung, where are you going?

711
00:47:36,815 --> 00:47:38,233
Granny, where are you doing here?

712
00:47:38,442 --> 00:47:39,735
You're getting better
with you tuberculosis.

713
00:47:39,943 --> 00:47:42,196
So mind you catch a cold,
have you taken your medicine?

714
00:47:42,279 --> 00:47:45,073
Yes, you're going to
fight with someone again?

715
00:47:45,157 --> 00:47:46,074
No.

716
00:47:46,283 --> 00:47:47,409
Don't go.

717
00:47:47,534 --> 00:47:48,660
I'm not fighting with anyone.

718
00:47:49,328 --> 00:47:51,997
- Don't go fighting.
- I'm not.

719
00:47:52,206 --> 00:47:56,418
Granny, he isn't going to fight,
he's going to act in a play.

720
00:47:56,668 --> 00:47:59,755
That Neighbour Theatre,
we're playing "Thunder Storm".

721
00:48:00,047 --> 00:48:01,465
"Thunder Storm"? It's a good play.

722
00:48:01,632 --> 00:48:03,759
Bruce Lee, Bark Yin,
Ng Chor Fan did it years ago.

723
00:48:03,884 --> 00:48:05,219
There was great response,

724
00:48:05,344 --> 00:48:06,762
so we're putting up one more show.

725
00:48:06,970 --> 00:48:08,514
We're hurrying for the rehearsal.

726
00:48:08,972 --> 00:48:10,724
You're acting in a play?

727
00:48:10,891 --> 00:48:12,184
Yes.

728
00:48:12,309 --> 00:48:18,440
Good, my grandson is an actor,
how smart he is!

729
00:48:19,775 --> 00:48:21,235
I'm very happy!

730
00:48:21,401 --> 00:48:23,737
OK, come on, go home now.

731
00:48:24,905 --> 00:48:28,534
She's put much saliva on my face.

732
00:48:29,034 --> 00:48:32,412
Your granny brought you up alone,
she's a real heroine.

733
00:48:32,621 --> 00:48:33,831
You're not.

734
00:48:37,167 --> 00:48:39,002
See how happy she is.

735
00:48:41,797 --> 00:48:45,175
Stop fighting anymore,
come and join our rehearsal.

736
00:48:52,641 --> 00:48:53,851
If you can defeat me,

737
00:48:54,017 --> 00:48:56,478
I'll swallow this plate.

738
00:48:56,687 --> 00:48:58,522
You aren't convinced?

739
00:48:59,398 --> 00:49:02,109
You should speak with stressing tone
"You aren't convinced?"

740
00:49:02,276 --> 00:49:04,653
This is raise my wrath from the inside.

741
00:49:04,820 --> 00:49:06,864
No need, as no one is watching.

742
00:49:06,989 --> 00:49:09,241
You suddenly want to play
"Fist of Fury".

743
00:49:09,449 --> 00:49:12,119
And make us to wear this costume,
this way is too much.

744
00:49:12,244 --> 00:49:15,038
I'm doing you a favour, right?

745
00:49:15,164 --> 00:49:17,624
- I only want to change the wig.
- Let's leave.

746
00:49:33,390 --> 00:49:35,434
That girl is pretty, your girlfriend?

747
00:49:35,642 --> 00:49:36,560
Sure.

748
00:49:36,768 --> 00:49:38,729
- Let's get serious, try again!
- Coming.

749
00:49:39,646 --> 00:49:41,273
If you can defeat me.

750
00:49:41,482 --> 00:49:44,693
I'll swallow this plate.

751
00:49:44,902 --> 00:49:47,488
You aren't convinced?

752
00:49:56,079 --> 00:49:57,623
Change the position, hurry.

753
00:50:45,838 --> 00:50:48,715
We're concentrated
when acting on the stage.

754
00:50:48,924 --> 00:50:51,176
It's dangerous if you suddenly rush up.

755
00:50:51,510 --> 00:50:54,179
I want to join you as you guys
were fevering up there.

756
00:50:54,429 --> 00:50:57,266
I chose "Fist Of Fury"
for some commercial reasons.

757
00:50:57,349 --> 00:50:59,852
Because there're fighting scenes,
