I didn't know being delivery boy
must answer so many questions.

1270
01:25:34,885 --> 01:25:36,011
Don't fucking fool me?

1271
01:25:36,303 --> 01:25:38,889
What are you doing? Are you a cop?

1272
01:25:39,097 --> 01:25:40,224
Yes, what's wrong?

1273
01:25:40,307 --> 01:25:41,725
I'm really a delivery boy.

1274
01:25:44,269 --> 01:25:47,564
Nothing...he's an idiot.

1275
01:25:47,815 --> 01:25:50,359
Search him if you don't believe.
Search him!

1276
01:25:52,820 --> 01:25:57,449
Kid, I let you go now,
be smart in future!

1277
01:26:03,413 --> 01:26:04,748
What is it?

1278
01:26:09,419 --> 01:26:11,380
Why did you do this?

1279
01:26:17,845 --> 01:26:19,596
What do you want?

1280
01:26:27,688 --> 01:26:28,897
What is it?

1281
01:26:32,609 --> 01:26:34,570
Want to harm me?

1282
01:27:13,650 --> 01:27:17,362
Sorry, I'm an undercover.

1283
01:27:30,751 --> 01:27:32,044
Cut.

1284
01:27:34,838 --> 01:27:35,756
How's that?

1285
01:27:36,006 --> 01:27:37,966
I'm fine, I'm still alive.

1286
01:27:38,133 --> 01:27:40,594
I mean my performance.

1287
01:27:40,886 --> 01:27:44,598
Very well, as this is your first time
being the leading actor.

1288
01:27:45,057 --> 01:27:46,350
Good take.

1289
01:27:48,060 --> 01:27:49,186
Thanks.

1290
01:27:49,686 --> 01:27:50,979
I'll call to police.

1291
01:27:52,648 --> 01:27:57,402
- Police!
- Freeze!

1292
01:27:57,486 --> 01:27:58,695
He's on my side...

1293
01:27:59,404 --> 01:28:00,614
Call the ambulance!

1294
01:28:10,290 --> 01:28:11,375
Piu Piu.

1295
01:28:13,085 --> 01:28:15,462
What's going on? It's dark already,
and you didn't give me a call?

1296
01:28:15,546 --> 01:28:17,297
- Shall I cook dinner for you?
- Just then I...

1297
01:28:17,381 --> 01:28:19,508
What's happen to you?
Didn't you play as the leading actor?

1298
01:28:19,716 --> 01:28:21,969
I don't care whether
you're a leading actor or an extra.

1299
01:28:22,136 --> 01:28:23,554
You must support my living forever.

1300
01:28:23,804 --> 01:28:25,931
Come on, try it
and see if it suits or not.

1301
01:28:26,473 --> 01:28:29,560
Red? Is it lipstick?
You're dating someone else?

1302
01:28:30,018 --> 01:28:31,353
I forgive you but...

1303
01:28:31,562 --> 01:28:34,231
I won't cook for you
if you dare next time, go!

1304
01:28:36,358 --> 01:28:39,444
What are you looking at?
Fight back, nuts!

1305
01:28:43,073 --> 01:28:45,742
Piu Piu, I love you.

1306
01:29:05,345 --> 01:29:06,430
Wait

1307
01:29:07,181 --> 01:29:09,349
You two mustn't get married!

1308
01:29:09,558 --> 01:29:10,559
Why?

1309
01:29:10,684 --> 01:29:13,187
Because you guys are brother and sister.

1310
01:29:14,313 --> 01:29:17,733
Sister, I'm sorry.

1311
01:29:18,025 --> 01:29:20,944
It's not your business,
I'm willing myself.

1312
01:29:21,153 --> 01:29:23,906
Your mood is wrong for this situation.

1313
01:29:24,114 --> 01:29:25,115
I've told you before.

1314
01:29:25,324 --> 01:29:28,827
Mood begins from your heart,
then goes to the outside of your body...

1315
01:29:28,994 --> 01:29:29,786
and returns to the heart, got it?

1316
01:29:29,953 --> 01:29:32,623
- Yes, got it.
- Don't be nervous.

1317
01:29:32,915 --> 01:29:34,208
I'm not nervous.

1318
01:29:34,708 --> 01:29:38,545
Sau, I think
the role of Master suits you more.

1319
01:29:38,670 --> 01:29:40,214
Why don't you play it?

1320
01:29:40,380 --> 01:29:43,675
Forget it, I'm not talented in acting.

1321
01:29:43,926 --> 01:29:45,761
I'd better be audience.

1322
01:29:46,470 --> 01:29:47,554
Not at all.

1323
01:29:47,638 --> 01:29:48,555
You're good.

1324
01:29:48,680 --> 01:29:50,766
Brother Sau,
audience are waiting outside.

1325
01:29:50,891 --> 01:29:51,892
- Are they?
- Hurry up.

1326
01:29:52,017 --> 01:29:53,852
- Take off your clothes first.
- For what?

1327
01:29:54,019 --> 01:29:54,812
I'll play it.

1328
01:29:54,978 --> 01:29:56,522
- Oh, no.
- Give it to me.

1329
01:29:56,647 --> 01:29:57,981
But you're not talented.

1330
01:29:58,106 --> 01:29:59,191
I'm not? Are you talented then?

1331
01:29:59,316 --> 01:30:00,400
I am.

1332
01:30:01,068 --> 01:30:02,277
Give it to me!

1333
01:30:03,111 --> 01:30:05,781
- No.
- Sau, stop fighting.

1334
01:30:05,948 --> 01:30:08,826
Stop fighting, eat potato chips,
why fighting for?

1335
01:30:27,052 --> 01:30:28,554
There're really many audience.

1336
01:30:28,762 --> 01:30:31,515
Sure, as we have special guests today.

1337
01:30:31,723 --> 01:30:33,475
Sister Cuckoo comes to help us today.

1338
01:30:35,102 --> 01:30:36,228
Thanks, Sister Cuckoo.

1339
01:30:36,353 --> 01:30:38,188
You're welcome, we finally have
the chance to act on the same stage.

1340
01:30:38,397 --> 01:30:39,439
Thanks!

1341
01:30:41,984 --> 01:30:43,569
Kung Hei Fat Choi! Thanks!

1342
01:30:43,777 --> 01:30:44,778
Happy New Year.

1343
01:30:44,945 --> 01:30:47,322
Congraduation! Everybody cheers up.

1344
01:30:47,406 --> 01:30:49,158
Thanks! Kung Hei!

